text: Adam Guy Gunthorpe (born 29 October 1983 in Australia) is a former first-class cricketer active 2005 who played in two matches for Hong Kong as a right- handed batsman.Adam Gunthorpe at ESPNcricinfoAdam Gunthorpe at CricketArchive ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Hong Kong cricketers
